:{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6814,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/21\/trial-hasan-husayn\/","url_meta":{"origin":28834,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Fitnah: Children are a trial, even for the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Buraydah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, was delivering a sermon when Hasan and Husayn came wearing red shirts, walking and tripping. The Prophet descended from the pulpit, picked them both up, and placed them in his lap. The Prophet said, \u201cAllah spoke the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18981,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/03\/prophet-refuge-hasan-husayn\/","url_meta":{"origin":28834,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet seeks refuge for Hasan and Husayn","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 3, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would seek refuge for his grandsons Hasan and Husayn, saying, \u201cVerily, your forefather would seek refuge for Ishmael and Isaac. I seek refuge in the perfect words of Allah from every devil and scourge and every harmful eye.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11080,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadith